sequenceDiagram
    actor User as KPMG User
    participant SPA as React SPA
    participant API as FastAPI /api/auth
    participant DB as PostgreSQL users table
    participant KV as Azure Key Vault
    participant AAD as Azure AD

    Note over User,AAD: BASELINE — Email + Password Auth (Current Pilot)

    User->>SPA: Enter email + password on /login
    SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/login { email, password }
    API->>DB: SELECT user_id, full_name, role, password, is_active WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>API: User row
    API->>API: Pilot: plaintext compare password == db.password<br/>PRODUCTION: bcrypt.verify(password, db.password_hash) cost=12

    alt Valid credentials AND is_active = true
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_log action=LOGIN
        API-->>SPA: 200 OK { user_id, email, full_name, role }
        SPA->>SPA: Store in React AppContext<br/>Pilot: localStorage<br/>PRODUCTION: in-memory only
        SPA-->>User: Redirect to /dashboard
    else Invalid credentials OR inactive account
        API-->>SPA: 401 Unauthorized { detail: Invalid credentials }
        SPA-->>User: Show error message
    end

    Note over User,AAD: PRODUCTION ADD-ON — JWT Token Issuance

    API->>KV: Read JWT_SECRET_KEY via Managed Identity
    KV-->>API: Secret value
    API->>API: jwt.encode sub=user_id role=role exp=now+15min
    API-->>SPA: access_token 15 min + refresh_token 7 days
    SPA->>SPA: access_token in memory<br/>refresh_token in HttpOnly cookie

    Note over User,AAD: TARGET ARCHITECTURE — Azure AD SSO + MFA

    User->>SPA: Click Sign in with KPMG SSO
    SPA->>AAD: Redirect to Azure AD OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Flow<br/>scopes: openid profile email<br/>client_id from App Registration
    AAD->>User: KPMG login page + MFA prompt via Conditional Access
    User->>AAD: KPMG credentials + MFA token Authenticator App
    AAD-->>SPA: Authorization Code short-lived
    SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/sso { code, redirect_uri }
    API->>AAD: POST token endpoint — exchange code for id_token + access_token
    AAD-->>API: id_token JWT with email, name, AD groups
    API->>API: Map AD group to IntelliSource role<br/>Upsert user record in PostgreSQL
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_log action=SSO_LOGIN
    API->>KV: Read JWT_SECRET_KEY
    API-->>SPA: IntelliSource JWT access_token 15 min<br/>refresh_token 7 days HttpOnly cookie
    SPA-->>User: Redirect to /dashboard
